eExam.18 Eye Assessment No No The assessment findings of the patient's eye examination. E16_21 Optional Element eExam.18 - Eye Assessment represents Version 2.2.1 elements E16_21 Eyes-Left Assessment and E16_22 Eyes-Right Assessment. The eye assessment value choices have been combined and expanded.
